# Phase 5: SaaS Architecture, KPI System & Financial Reports

> 目標：將 `enterprise-admin` 從單租戶 MVP 升級為可擴展 SaaS 架構，並建立對齊 `startup_template_pack` (文件 #11/#12/#13) 的完整營運 KPI 引擎與財務報表模組。

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Migration Strategy**: Phase 5 requires a schema migration from SQLite to PostgreSQL (as per ADR-001). This is a breaking change that needs a migration window.

> [!WARNING]
> **Multi-Tenancy Decision**: The plan proposes a **row-level isolation** (shared DB, `tenant_id` column) strategy for SaaS. If you prefer **schema-per-tenant** or **database-per-tenant**, please indicate before implementation begins.

> [!CAUTION]
> **Financial Data Accuracy**: The `Expense` model introduces manual data entry. Any automated connections to external accounting systems (QuickBooks, Xero) are deferred to Phase 6.

---

## Phase 5a: SaaS-Ready Architecture (基礎設施)

### 模組一：Multi-Tenancy Foundation

#### [NEW] `backend/src/lib/tenant.ts`
- `TenantContext` middleware: extracts `tenant_id` from JWT claims or `X-Tenant-Id` header
- Prisma middleware that **auto-injects** `tenant_id` on all [create](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/src/modules/orders/order.controller.ts#5-16) operations and `where` clauses

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20(1)/0.專案/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)
- Add `Tenant` model:
  ```
  model Tenant {
    id        String @id @default(uuid())
    name      String
    slug      String @unique  // subdomain identifier
    plan      String @default("free") // free | starter | pro
    settings  String? // JSON config
    createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  }
  ```
- Add `tenantId String @map("tenant_id")` + `@@index([tenantId])` to: [User](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/src/modules/users/users.service.ts#5-210), [Customer](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/crm.ts#3-12), [Product](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/inventory.ts#14-25), [Supplier](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/inventory.ts#3-13), [Order](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/orders.ts#16-33), [Interaction](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/src/modules/crm/crm.controller.ts#47-55), `AuditLog`

#### [NEW] [adr_006_saas_multi_tenancy.md](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20(1)/0.專案/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/infrastructure/adr/adr_006_saas_multi_tenancy.md)
- ADR documenting the row-level isolation decision, trade-offs vs schema-per-tenant, and data leakage prevention strategy

### 模組二：Plan-Based Feature Gating

#### [NEW] `backend/src/middleware/plan.middleware.ts`
- `requirePlan('pro')` middleware: checks tenant's plan level before allowing access to premium features (e.g., financial reports, advanced KPIs)

#### [MODIFY] [AdminLayout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20(1)/0.專案/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/layouts/AdminLayout.tsx)
- Conditionally render sidebar items based on `tenant.plan` from auth context  
