## Phase 5b: Operational KPI Engine (營運 KPI 指標系統)

> 對齊 `startup_template_pack` 文件 #11（營運KPI與儀表板模板）和 #12（單位經濟模型模板）

### KPI Metrics Schema

#### [NEW] `backend/src/modules/analytics/analytics.service.ts`
Unified analytics engine computing these KPIs from live transactional data:

| KPI | Formula | Source Tables | Alert Threshold |
|-----|---------|--------------|-----------------|
| **gross_margin_pct** | [(revenue - COGS) / revenue × 100](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/App.tsx#27-62) | [OrderItem](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/orders.ts#5-15) × `Product.costPrice` | < 24% |
| **ccc_days** | `DIO + DSO - DPO` | `InventoryTransaction`, [Order](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/orders.ts#16-33) | > 35 |
| **cac_twd** | `marketing_spend / new_customers` | `Expense(type=MARKETING)`, [Customer](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/crm.ts#3-12) | > 220 |
| **aov_twd** | `total_revenue / total_orders` | [Order](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/orders.ts#16-33) | — |
| **repurchase_rate** | `repeat_customers / total_customers × 100` | [Customer(purchaseCount>1)](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/api/crm.ts#3-12) | < 20% |
| **ltv_twd** | `AOV × margin × freq × retention_months` | Computed from above | — |
| **bonus_gate_pass** | `margin≥30 AND ccc≤30 AND incidents=0` | Computed | false |

#### [NEW] `backend/src/modules/analytics/analytics.controller.ts`
- `GET /api/v1/admin/analytics/kpis?period=2026-W12` — weekly/monthly snapshot  
- `GET /api/v1/admin/analytics/trends?from=2026-01&to=2026-06` — time series for charting

#### [NEW] `backend/src/modules/analytics/analytics.routes.ts`
- Protected with [authMiddleware](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/src/middleware/auth.middleware.ts#5-66) + `requirePermission('read:analytics')`

#### [MODIFY] [seed.ts](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20(1)/0.專案/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/prisma/seed.ts)
- Add `read:analytics` and `manage:analytics` permissions to SUPER_ADMIN

