## Phase 5c: Financial & Reporting Module (財務與報表模組)

> 對齊 `startup_template_pack` 文件 #13（三年財務模型_月度模板）

### 模組一：毛利分析 (Gross Margin Analysis)

#### [NEW] `backend/src/modules/reports/margin.service.ts`
- `getMarginByProduct(period)` — per-SKU: [(retailPrice - costPrice) / retailPrice](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/App.tsx#27-62)
- `getMarginByCategory(period)` — per-category aggregate
- `getMarginTrend(from, to)` — monthly margin % time series
- Data source: `OrderItem JOIN Product` with actual sold quantities

#### [NEW] `admin-ui/src/pages/Reports/MarginAnalysisPage.tsx`
- **Top section**: Overall margin gauge (current month vs target 28.6%)
- **Table**: Per-product margin breakdown with sortable columns (Revenue, COGS, Margin %, Contribution %)
- **Chart**: Monthly margin trend line (6-month window)

### 模組二：現金流 (Cash Flow Tracking)

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20(1)/0.專案/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)
- Add `Expense` model for manual OPEX tracking:
  ```
  model Expense {
    id          String   @id @default(uuid())
    type        String   // RENT | SALARY | MARKETING | LOGISTICS | OTHER
    amount      Float
    description String?
    period      String   // YYYY-MM
    createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  }
  ```

#### [NEW] `backend/src/modules/reports/cashflow.service.ts`
- `getCashFlowStatement(period)`:
  - **營運現金流**: `Order revenue collected` − `Expense outflows`
  - **庫存投資**: Sum of `InventoryTransaction(type=IN)` × `Product.costPrice`
  - **期末現金**: Roll-forward from configurable opening balance
- `getCashFlowTrend(from, to)` — monthly P&L waterfall data

#### [NEW] `admin-ui/src/pages/Reports/CashFlowPage.tsx`
- **Summary cards**: 期初現金 → 營運現金流 → 期末現金
- **Waterfall chart**: Revenue inflows vs expense outflows by category
- **Table**: Monthly cash flow roll-forward (aligned with doc #13 format)

### 模組三：產品銷售排行 (Product Sales Ranking)

#### [NEW] `backend/src/modules/reports/sales-ranking.service.ts`
- `getTopProducts(period, limit)` — by revenue, by quantity, by margin contribution
- `getProductPerformance(productId, from, to)` — individual SKU deep-dive: sales velocity, stock turnover (DIO), projected stockout date

#### [NEW] `admin-ui/src/pages/Reports/SalesRankingPage.tsx`
- **Leaderboard**: Top 10 products by revenue with sparkline trend
- **Category breakdown**: Pie/Donut chart by product category
- **Table**: Full ranking with Revenue, Qty Sold, Margin %, Stock Days remaining

### 模組四：Report Routes & Navigation

#### [NEW] `backend/src/modules/reports/reports.controller.ts`
- Unified controller for margin, cashflow, and ranking endpoints

#### [NEW] `backend/src/modules/reports/reports.routes.ts`
- `GET /api/v1/admin/reports/margin?period=2026-03`
- `GET /api/v1/admin/reports/cashflow?period=2026-03`
- `GET /api/v1/admin/reports/cashflow/trend?from=...&to=...`
- `GET /api/v1/admin/reports/sales-ranking?period=2026-03&sort=revenue&limit=10`
- Protected with `requirePermission('read:reports')`

#### [MODIFY] [App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20(1)/0.專案/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/App.tsx)
- Add routes: `/reports/margin`, `/reports/cashflow`, `/reports/sales-ranking`

#### [MODIFY] [AdminLayout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20(1)/0.專案/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/admin-ui/src/layouts/AdminLayout.tsx)
- New sidebar section: **"Financial Reports"** with sub-items for each report page

