## Data Architecture (新增 Models 總覽)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    Tenant ||--o{ User : "has"
    Tenant ||--o{ Customer : "has"
    Tenant ||--o{ Product : "has"
    Tenant ||--o{ Order : "has"
    Tenant ||--o{ Expense : "has"
    
    Order ||--|{ OrderItem : "contains"
    OrderItem }|--|| Product : "references"
    Product ||--|{ InventoryTransaction : "tracks"
    
    Expense }o--|| Tenant : "belongs to"
    
    Order }|--|| Customer : "placed by"
    Customer ||--|{ Interaction : "has"
```

| Model | Status | Key Fields |
|-------|--------|------------|
| `Tenant` | 🆕 NEW | [id](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/src/middleware/validate.middleware.ts#4-42), `name`, `slug`, `plan`, `settings` |
| `Expense` | 🆕 NEW | [id](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive%20-%20MSFT%20%281%29/0.%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88/startup/systems/enterprise-admin/backend/src/middleware/validate.middleware.ts#4-42), `type`, `amount`, `period`, `tenantId` |
| Existing models | ✏️ MODIFY | Add `tenantId` column |

